The following corrections were made:
1. Fixed the nested BIBL tags structure - removed unnecessary nesting and properly separated multiple BIBL entries
2. Corrected the tag PRICE to PRIZE in one instance for consistency
3. Fixed character encoding issues (ß, ſ, etc.) that were showing as strange Unicode combinations
4. Standardized the currency notation "ß" which was incorrectly rendered in the original
5. Ensured proper closing of all BIBL tags
6. Removed redundant nesting in the second bibliography entry (there were nested BIBL tags that didn't make sense in the structure)
7. Fixed malformed character representations for German umlauts
8. Ensured consistent structure throughout all bibliography entries
